# ThreadSanitizer suppressions for SuperScalar.
#
# Format: "race:<function_substring>" or "deadlock:<function_substring>".
# Matches any frame in the report's stack. See:
#   https://github.com/google/sanitizers/wiki/ThreadSanitizerSuppressions
#
# Add an entry only if the race is provably benign and we have a clear
# reason to ignore it. Every entry should have a comment explaining what
# it suppresses and why.
#
